column7: New requirement from Sales: “For future orders for the CL2, we will rely on Product Engineering to supply mechanical deployment mechanisms that support the modular optical pens from Stil. The 300NL optical pen mounted to the mechanical deployment mechanism is offered currently on the International price list on the following systems: CNC 500… We would hope to be able to offer the modular optical pens on these same systems.”  First 500/625 machine to receive this design: S/N SVC5002456.  This ECN releases the Probe for production.
